# LiveCord Welcome Bot

A professional Discord welcome bot with embed editing, invite tracking, and Mimu-style UI.

## Features

- **Welcome System** - Send custom text messages or embeds when members join
- **Embed Editor** - Create and edit embeds with an easy modal interface
- **Text + Embed Together** - Use `{embed:name}` in welcome messages
- **Placeholders** - `{user}`, `{username}`, `{server}`, `{server_icon}`, `{user_avatar}`, `{member_count}`
- **Prefix Commands** - `&help`, `&embed`, `&welcome`, `&test`, `&ping`, `&serverinfo`
- **Slash Commands** - `/help`, `/embed`, `/welcome`, `/test`, `/ping`, `/serverinfo`
- **Professional Help Menu** - Select menu to browse modules
- **MongoDB Database** - Persistent storage for embeds and settings

## Commands

### Prefix: `&`

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `&help` | Show help menu with select menu |
| `&ping` | Check bot latency |
| `&serverinfo` | Show detailed server information |
| `&embed create <name>` | Create a new embed |
| `&embed edit <name>` | Edit an embed (opens modal) |
| `&embed list` | List all saved embeds |
| `&embed delete <name>` | Delete an embed |
| `&embed show <name>` | Show an embed preview |
| `&welcome channel #channel` | Set welcome channel |
| `&welcome toggle true/false` | Enable/disable welcome messages |
| `&welcome message <text>` | Set welcome message (supports `{embed:name}`) |
| `&welcome embed <name>` | Use only an embed for welcome |
| `&test` | Test welcome message |

### Slash: `/`

All prefix commands also work as slash commands.

